Building
========

The oblsc sofware requires glib-2.0. At the time of writing the author
uses version 2.26.1.

Reporting Bugs
==============

Please use the issue tracker at https://github.com/frej/oblsc/issues
before sending an email to the author.

Contributing
============

The public Git repository is located at
https://github.com/frej/oblsc. Please use the github facilities for
submitting contributions.
